<p>Special thanks to Metaphysician and minmin for approving of and supporting my re-interpretation of their skips. Aslo thanks to AidenEldritch, nox, TwistedGears, AetherialSkies, Lex1nat0r, SleepLight, NineVolt, shaggydredlocks, Roget, Petrograd, Conwell, Gaffsey, Kieraaa and others if I unfortunately left out any for reviewing the draft :3</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Actually an excuse for more god shipping :P</span></p>

