<p>I'm not really into this, largely due to personal foibles: The imagery is cool, but grand high fantasy religious content isn't really my thing.</p>
<p>I do think combining the two SCPs in question and the antagonist of the antimemetics tales is <em>brilliant</em>, and I'm glad you're done so. It just happens that as we discussed in chat, you have a different interpretation of fifthism than the original SCP, which is fine (I'm not big on the Scientology angle either), but you've taken it in a direction that doesn't do much for me.</p>
<p>So, cool imagery, very cool idea, but no vote.</p>

